## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="d6259-102">O <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> e <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> juntos, propriedades determinam como os usuários podem selecionar itens em um <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6259-102">The <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> properties together determine how users can select items in a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="d6259-103">Por exemplo, se o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> é o único e o <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> é <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit>, o usuário pode selecionar uma célula de cada vez no <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit.Cell>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6259-103">For example, if the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionMode%2A> is Single and the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGrid.SelectionUnit%2A> is <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit>, the user can select one cell at a time in the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.DataGridSelectionUnit.Cell>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="d6259-104">Modo inExtended, selecione vários itens mantendo pressionada a tecla SHIFT para estender a seleção de um ponto de ancoragem ou as teclas CTRL chave individualmente para selecionar itens adicionais.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="d6259-104">InExtended mode, select multiple items by holding down the SHIFT key to extend the selection from an anchor point or the CTRL key to individually select additional items.</span></span>  
  
